{"tid":1941151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"留學生瘋狂返港一事咪證明移民唔理支那搞搞震係無撚用","createTime":"2020-03-24T08:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T06:34:39.000Z","uid":65328,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"14ee86171f4a2927940ca92b99ccb90769f2643e","tid":1941151,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T08:40:58.000Z","msg":"留學生瘋狂返港一事咪證明移民唔理支那搞搞震係無撚用<br />\n<br />\n藍絲成日話唔鐘意支那就離開，<br />\n我一早已經屌佢地移民唔抵抗支那任由支那作惡， 就算移民都係會無用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔抵抗支那只移民只會有以下結果<br />\n第一， 支那會不停輸出邪惡， 最終連外國都不能幸免<br />\n<br />\n第二， 外國人民深受支那其害， 實有極右拎東亞人樣祭旗， 就算未去到暴力程度， 都會有歧視憎恨<br />\n<br />\n所以以後可以咁搏班藍絲d戇鳩廢話"},{"pid":"59dfef3432b7abfb2c891e4ee4030f0ac487ef5c","tid":1941151,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T08:42:18.000Z","msg":"留學生瘋狂返港一事證明香港俾佢地害到社區爆發"},{"pid":"269d252b36d636e4ec7817c4f03003fd7837dae7","tid":1941151,"uid":132174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T08:42:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>會員新人類訴求一 </ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n收回強姦犯心態言論並道歉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KbNWHdK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKbNWHdK.jpg&h=4552f2df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但有證據顯示新人類有機會的確有強姦犯心理<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HyOiVyT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHyOiVyT.jpg&h=4a37d5f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>訴求二</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n要求絲打被白人騷擾時一定要報警 如果唔係就係崇洋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ovpQ7J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ovpQ7J.jpg&h=466517a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Bonus</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n爭取全港男士喺婦女節獲得一份小禮物 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LmeBHeW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLmeBHeW.jpg&h=8d82aa72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果喺八點前訴求得唔到回應 將會有升級行動</span></strong>"},{"pid":"341dfed454abbcfe14609fd47c59d8d2ad58b396","tid":1941151,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T08:43:31.000Z","msg":"本來就係，消滅唔到支那去邊都奶野（台灣除外）<br />\n<br />\n大家繼續國際戰線追擊支那，將全球人怒火放返去支那，咪比支共同班賤畜扮無野<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助全球爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1936004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1936004</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e9fbae6d92bdb7a31e48037e8f15bb246f390938","tid":1941151,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"269d252b36d636e4ec7817c4f03003fd7837dae7","tid":1941151,"uid":132174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T08:42:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>會員新人類訴求一 </ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n收回強姦犯心態言論並道歉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KbNWHdK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKbNWHdK.jpg&h=4552f2df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但有證據顯示新人類有機會的確有強姦犯心理<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HyOiVyT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHyOiVyT.jpg&h=4a37d5f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>訴求二</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n要求絲打被白人騷擾時一定要報警 如果唔係就係崇洋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ovpQ7J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ovpQ7J.jpg&h=466517a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Bonus</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n爭取全港男士喺婦女節獲得一份小禮物 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LmeBHeW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLmeBHeW.jpg&h=8d82aa72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果喺八點前訴求得唔到回應 將會有升級行動</span></strong>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"你講吓你既升級係點樣"},{"pid":"61e321097a9c77dc79e92d54573cda909aeab4a5","tid":1941151,"uid":132174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9fbae6d92bdb7a31e48037e8f15bb246f390938","tid":1941151,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0